    },
    "Purpose: Build basic description skills\nGoal: Clearly describe people, objects, and places in 90 seconds." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "作用：建立基础描述能力\n目标：90秒清晰说人、物、地。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Purpose: Cover real-life communication scenarios\nGoal: Make requests, refuse, and negotiate with tact." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "作用：覆盖真实服务沟通场景\n目标：提出需求、拒绝和协商时保持分寸。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Purpose: Enter opinion and comparison topics\nGoal: Express views with flexibility, avoiding extremes." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "作用：进入观点题与比较题\n目标：表达立场时保留弹性，不走极端。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Purpose: Enter workplace context and responsibility\nGoal: Report, explain, and handle disagreements steadily." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "作用：进入工作语境和责任表达\n目标：汇报、解释和分歧沟通都更稳。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Purpose: Explain processes and decision-making\nGoal: Clearly describe steps, trade-offs, and judgment logic." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "作用：解释做事过程与决策依据\n目标：说清步骤、取舍和判断逻辑。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Purpose: Integrate experience and values into coherent expression\nGoal: Reflect on change and discuss future uncertainty." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "作用：把经验和价值整合成闭环表达\n目标：回顾变化，也能谈未来的不确定性。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Purpose: Practice authentic but measured interpersonal expression\nGoal: Support, refuse, apologize, and express concern naturally." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "作用：练真实但克制的人际表达\n目标：支持、拒绝、道歉和担忧都说得自然。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Purpose: Train event narration and initial reflection\nGoal: Tell what happened and why it matters." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "作用：训练事件讲述与初步反思\n目标：把发生了什么、为什么重要说完整。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Purpose: Transition to abstract value discussions\nGoal: Discuss ideas without being vague." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "作用：过渡到抽象价值讨论\n目标：能谈理念，但不空泛。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
